Markw wrote
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
A minor problem visible on the home page
&amp;lt;&lt;a class="ext-link" href="http://s031.okserver.org:2375/"&gt;&lt;span class="icon"&gt;â€‹&lt;/span&gt;http://s031.okserver.org:2375/&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt; and other pages, when viewing in both
Chrome and Firefox:
&lt;/p&gt;
